Enhance my existing academic platform (which already includes report generation, lesson planner, and research report modules) by adding an Attendance-Based Post-Class Feedback System.

You can either integrate this into the current dashboard or create a separate module, whichever results in a cleaner and more scalable design.

Requirements:

1. Roles & Authentication:
- Support three roles: Faculty, Student, Admin
- Students must log in to access their dashboard
- Use role-based access control

2. Student Dataset:
- Maintain a structured student database with fields:
  student_id, name, email, department, year
- Each student should be uniquely identifiable

3. Class & Attendance Management:
- Faculty should be able to:
  - Create/select a class session (course, date)
  - View list of enrolled students
  - Mark attendance (Present/Absent) via UI (checkbox or toggle)
- Store attendance with:
  class_id, student_id, status (present/absent), marked_by (faculty_id), timestamp

4. Feedback Access Control (Critical Logic):
- Students should only be able to give feedback if:
  - They are marked as "present" for that class
- If absent:
  - Feedback option must be hidden or disabled
- Prevent duplicate feedback submissions per class per student

5. Student Dashboard:
- After login, students should see:
  - List of attended classes
  - “Give Feedback” button only for eligible classes
- Feedback form should include:
  - Rating (1–5)
  - Comments
  - Suggestions (optional)

6. Anonymity & Visibility:
- Faculty should see only anonymous feedback (no student identity)
- Admin should see full details:
  student_id, timestamp, feedback content

7. Database Design:
- Create and relate tables:
  students, classes, attendance, feedback
- Ensure proper foreign key relationships
- Enforce one feedback per student per class

8. Integration:
- Link feedback data to existing report generation module
- Allow reports to include:
  - average rating
  - feedback summary
  - insights

9. UI/UX:
- Faculty: Attendance marking interface
- Student: Clean feedback submission interface
- Admin: Full visibility dashboard

10. Optional Enhancements:
- Add submission deadline for feedback after class
- Show feedback submission status (pending/submitted)
- Add simple analytics (average ratings per class)

Build this as a scalable, clean, production-ready module that integrates seamlessly with the existing system.	

